data.description: Assumable VA Loan at 2.25%.  Wind down the crushed asphalt driveway and be swept away by the majesty of two meticulously maintained acres with forest service on two sides! This beautifully updated custom home has an attached 2 car garage, fully fenced back yard, a detached shop with 50-amp hook-ups.  The finished walkout basement has a separate entry & second living area with one bed/bath that is perfect for teens, parents or income opportunity.  Recently painted, wood stoves in the shop and house, new deck, updated kitchen and flooring are just as stunning as the sunsets, stargazing and views.  Relax on your private deck or in your jacuzzi on the secluded patio that is perfect for entertaining or watching wildlife.  This turn-key home has it all and is a must see!
